\af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5833606\charrsid3422972 The Windows Server VM running on VirtualBox with a static IP address of 192.168.56.10 on the host-only 
adapter setting of VirtualBox named as Ethernet, and a NAT adapter named as Ethernet 2 for internet access. PowerShell 7 must be running with admin privileges for scripts to execute and make changes in the system. The first step in executing the scripts o
n the system is to clone }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5440959\charrsid3422972 them}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5833606\charrsid3422972  from GitHub. 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid5833606\charrsid3422972 Clone the repository:
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5833606\charrsid3422972 Git clone }{\field\fldedit{\*\fldinst {\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid807816  HYPERLINK "https://github.com/Studywithme-wq/BarmBuzz" }}{\fldrslt {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 
