\af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4268954\charrsid3422972 If AD service tests fail, check Evidence\\HealthChecks\\
dcdiag_final.txt for NTDS or DNS errors. Such errors are most commonly caused by time synchronization issues. If organizational units (OUs) tests fail, verify the DependsOn chain and check Evidence\\DSC\\*_apply_verbose.txt.
\par  If GPO link tests fail, SYSVOL may not have been ready. Thus, re-running the build resolves this. If FGPP tests fail, verify the domain functional level is WinThreshold using Get-ADDomain | Select-Object DomainMode.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11288052\charrsid3422972 
