The password policy applied is to ensure maximum security, reliability, and ease of use of the system. The PSO-Admins policy applies a minimum 16-character password, with 24-password history. The maximum age of the password is 30 days with 3 attempts lock
out. This helps secure GG-IT-Admins and GG-Derby-IT-Admins from unauthorized access from third parties. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16152353\charrsid3422972 This rule is applied to all }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid535152\charrsid3422972 accounts}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16152353\charrsid3422972  through }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid535152\charrsid3422972 the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16152353\charrsid3422972 default domain policy. This is possible due to FGPP because without it, it }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid535152\charrsid3422972 would}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16152353\charrsid3422972 
 be burdensome for}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid535152\charrsid3422972  end u
sers or privileged accounts to receive an insignificantly strong policy. FGPP prevents this situation without using new or separate domains and only uses the default domain for all groups to enforce the policies}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 
